segmentation.p: Seperate files have been created for each movement of the work.
This file contains the eight movement of the work.

normalization.p: Normalizations of dynamics have been individually marked using the MEI Editorial Markup.
The direction of stems from the third stave line upwards has been individually regulated downwards and marked using the MEI Editorial Markup.
Normalizations of different directions of stems within a beam-element have been individually marked using the MEI Editorial Markup.
Breaks between syllables have been encoded with dashes.

correction.p: Errors and their corrections have been individually marked using the MEI Editorial Markup.

editorialDecl.p: The designation of the movement has not been seperately edited for every single staff, but has been encoded in the titleStmt as subtitles. Note, that "Canto" is the only voice, in which the designation (Largo) differs from the other voices (Andante). The tempo "Andante" was chosen, because from six voices, five have the designation "Andante" (Vl. 1, Vl. 2, Vla., Vlne., Org.) and only "Canto" diverges.
